description: The Famiresu Senshi are a super-sentai team. In their normal lives, they work as waitresses at A La Mode, a family restaurant (famiresu). Originally assembled by http://anidb.net/ch43694 [Shuuta]`s father, they are now led by Shuuta and http://anidb.net/ch43692 [Chiyoko], the manager and assistant manager.
name: Famiresu Senshi
